Immerse yourself in the memories of Trump, in his dreams as a young, star-struck jazz musician, in love with the lovely Lady Poppy.

Presenting a daring parallel with the real story of Louis Armstrong, relive Trump's life, his quest to form a group, his love affair and battle against injustice in the New Orleans of the early 20th century.

Let inspiration guide you through this fascinating platform game.

FEATURES:

- Polished platformer with high quality jazz music! 
- Beautiful graphics, controls are easy and the gameplay is fun and addicting 
- Length of play approximately 3 hours, or more!
- Move around New Orleans depicted with stylish graphics 
- Follow young Trump's moving story and be part of the birth of jazz music.
- Enjoy the original jazzy soundtrack specially composed by jazz musicians
- Use your trumpet to stop time
- Brave all the dangers and traps, with bosses, moving platforms, cops, spikes, and much more
